data.description: This property offers you a meticulously built home that meets all your needs. Built in 2021, this home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, providing ample space for your family and guests. The spacious kitchen is perfect for cooking and entertaining, with plenty of storage. Step out onto the covered deck off the dining room and enjoy outdoor dining. Inside, you'll find an open floor plan that allows for seamless flow and comfortable living. The split bedroom design ensures privacy and tranquility. The walk-out basement boasts a large family room, storage areas, and even a dedicated John Deere room for all your equipment storage needs. Enjoy a home that provides you with a living space that combines functionality, comfort, and style.
